1
00:00:24,030 --> 00:00:25,290
[Adapted from a novel published on
Qidian Reading under China Literature]

2
00:00:25,320 --> 00:00:27,180
["Way of Choices" by Mao Ni]

3
00:00:28,300 --> 00:00:29,830
[Minors]

4
00:00:29,860 --> 00:00:31,550
[should watch with guardian consent]

5
00:02:14,530 --> 00:02:19,410
[Way of Choices]

6
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:22,760
Must we go?

7
00:02:21,640 --> 00:02:24,870
[Previously]

8
00:02:23,079 --> 00:02:25,640
This is the best arrangement.

9
00:02:25,720 --> 00:02:27,160
The streets outside are full of soldiers.

10
00:02:27,160 --> 00:02:28,280
They're not friendly.

11
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:28,840
Form up.

12
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:30,350
Kill them all!

13
00:02:30,600 --> 00:02:32,620
There's no need for you

14
00:02:32,770 --> 00:02:34,520
to handle this trash yourself.

15
00:02:34,640 --> 00:02:35,990
Jin Yulyu,

16
00:02:36,160 --> 00:02:38,420
do you intend to defy the Emperor's will?

17
00:02:38,480 --> 00:02:40,480
I answer only to Her Highness now!

18
00:02:41,079 --> 00:02:42,800
A childish quarrel that goes too far

19
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,130
is hardly appropriate.

20
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:47,430
It's another era of wildflowers in bloom.

21
00:02:48,079 --> 00:02:50,410
The warning talisman has been triggered?

22
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:05,560
Why are you here?

23
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:10,400
Her Majesty asked me to watch them

24
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:12,200
so that they wouldn't go too far.

25
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,480
How did I fall asleep?

26
00:03:16,760 --> 00:03:17,160
You...

27
00:03:17,380 --> 00:03:18,780
What are you trying to do?

28
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,480
It's not hygienic to go to bed in clothes.

29
00:03:20,480 --> 00:03:21,340
I need to clean.

30
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:22,040
Excuse me.

31
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:23,160
You...

32
00:03:23,210 --> 00:03:24,340
You think I'm dirty?

33
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:27,040
If it weren't for the strange fragrance

34
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:27,960
that made people sleepy,

35
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:29,120
I wouldn't have lain here!

36
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:30,180
You're not sleepy.

37
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:31,170
You're sick.

38
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:34,400
You are sick.

39
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:38,440
I didn't know

40
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:40,600
you cared so much about your appearance.

41
00:03:40,600 --> 00:03:42,720
You have such
a big bronze mirror in the room.

42
00:03:42,720 --> 00:03:44,280
A bronze mirror helps one
tidy their appearance

43
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:45,480
and refine their virtue.

44
00:03:45,480 --> 00:03:45,920
Here.

45
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:47,440
Too worried to sleep.

46
00:03:46,870 --> 00:03:48,850
[Too worried to sleep;
sweating due to Lung Heat]

47
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:48,800
Sweating due to Lung Heat.

48
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:49,640
Yin and Yang are not balanced.

49
00:03:48,850 --> 00:03:50,829
[Unbalanced Yin & Yang] [Changsheng]

50
00:03:50,160 --> 00:03:51,690
Do you have these symptoms?

51
00:03:51,880 --> 00:03:52,800
Make congee with Job's tears

52
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:53,960
and mix thick slices of notoginseng in it.

53
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,160
It can calm your nerves, help you sleep,

54
00:03:55,160 --> 00:03:56,440
and reduce night sweats.

55
00:03:56,440 --> 00:03:57,000
Take it.

56
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:00,080
My health condition

57
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:01,480
is none of your business!

58
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:08,280
The palace has rejected

59
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:10,360
Luo's request to participate in
the Imperial Court Exam.

60
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,280
She's in Li Palace.

61
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:12,680
She won't come out again.

62
00:04:13,750 --> 00:04:17,910
[Follow Your Heart]

63
00:04:15,600 --> 00:04:16,880
Luo is my student.

64
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:19,050
Looks like I need to go to Li Palace.

65
00:04:19,459 --> 00:04:21,510
[Follow Your Heart]

66
00:04:22,320 --> 00:04:24,470
[Li Palace of the State Religion]

67
00:04:27,960 --> 00:04:30,140
[Excellence and Virtue]

68
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:37,360
They don't seem to be very kind.

69
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:42,880
Senior Su.

70
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:45,060
Greetings, Senior Su.

71
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:47,120
Senior Su has always hated

72
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,159
fame-seekers.

73
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:51,240
Chen's going to have a hard time!

74
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:55,070
[Su Moyu, the First Genius
of the Li Palace Affiliate]

75
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:53,120
Turn back.

76
00:04:53,840 --> 00:04:54,480
Today,

77
00:04:54,960 --> 00:04:56,760
you won't be entering Li Palace.

78
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:58,940
I'm here to see my student,

79
00:04:59,080 --> 00:05:00,520
not to fight with others.

80
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:02,000
You've only reached
the Realm of Marrow Cleansing.

81
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:05,040
How dare you call yourself director
of the State Religious Academy?

82
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:05,840
How arrogant!

83
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:10,240
Furthermore,

84
00:05:10,400 --> 00:05:12,070
I'm more disappointed

85
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:14,770
you didn't even enter the Blue Cloud List.

86
00:05:14,840 --> 00:05:16,060
You're not on the list,

87
00:05:16,060 --> 00:05:17,660
yet you became the director.

88
00:05:18,520 --> 00:05:20,720
It's a disgrace to our state religtion.

89
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:23,940
Stop pretending!

90
00:05:24,080 --> 00:05:25,360
Is it important to be on the list?

91
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,170
Shut up.

92
00:05:27,030 --> 00:05:30,400
The State Religious Academy's the orthodox
institution of our state religion.

93
00:05:30,400 --> 00:05:31,760
I regard it as my model.

94
00:05:32,300 --> 00:05:33,500
Since it's orthodox,

95
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:35,480
how can we let the incompetent person

96
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:37,070
to defile it?

97
00:05:40,080 --> 00:05:42,320
Princess Luo is in the Green Leaf World.

98
00:05:42,520 --> 00:05:44,920
It happens that my master
ordered me to guard the entrance.

99
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,250
If you want to visit her,

100
00:05:46,320 --> 00:05:47,850
you have to defeat me first.

101
00:05:48,250 --> 00:05:49,280
Shameless!

102
00:05:49,520 --> 00:05:50,520
Shame on you, who's reached
the Realm of Seated Illumination,

103
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:53,920
for challenging someone with
the Realm of Marrow Cleansing!

104
00:05:54,159 --> 00:05:55,159
Please advise me.

105
00:05:56,500 --> 00:05:58,190
You have some guts.

106
00:05:58,780 --> 00:05:59,980
In this competition,

107
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,520
I won't use my True Essence.

108
00:06:01,520 --> 00:06:02,210
Take this!

109
00:06:20,820 --> 00:06:23,280
Something's wrong with his swordsmanship.

110
00:06:24,690 --> 00:06:26,040
He's using the sword as a brush,

111
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:29,300
tracing the Li Palace Sword Formation
with sword slashes.

112
00:06:33,750 --> 00:06:35,500
[Seal the Evil, Li Palace Sword Formation]

113
00:06:35,640 --> 00:06:36,800
With the Seated Illumination,

114
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:38,720
he draw such a perfect
Li Palace Sword Formation.

115
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:40,560
Senior Su truly lives up to his name.

116
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:42,080
Your footwork is impressive,

117
00:06:42,080 --> 00:06:44,080
but I've trapped you with the formation.

118
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:45,040
Chen Changsheng,

119
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:46,460
you can go home

120
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:48,360
and reflect on yourself.

121
00:06:51,880 --> 00:06:52,580
Chen Changsheng,

122
00:06:52,580 --> 00:06:53,640
what are you doing?

123
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:55,000
Get out of the formation!

124
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,080
It's useless.

125
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:58,480
The Li Palace Sword Formation was created
by the current Grand Pontiff.

126
00:06:58,480 --> 00:07:00,690
It's impossible to escape
once it's formed.

127
00:07:00,690 --> 00:07:02,160
According to The Record of Misty Splendor,

128
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:03,400
the Li Palace Sword Formation

129
00:07:03,400 --> 00:07:04,480
has 13 forms

130
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,560
and is exquisite.

131
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:07,560
However, he didn't use his True Essence

132
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:08,990
and demanded excessive precision,

133
00:07:08,990 --> 00:07:10,390
which exposed the flaws.

134
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:12,140
So, this problem

135
00:07:12,400 --> 00:07:14,130
is actually very easy to solve.

136
00:07:14,320 --> 00:07:15,070
Kill!

137
00:07:26,210 --> 00:07:27,140
Watch out above!

138
00:07:47,960 --> 00:07:49,560
The sword formation is done.

139
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:50,680
You're lost.

140
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:52,760
Is that true?

141
00:07:55,840 --> 00:07:57,300
Last attack!

142
00:07:58,080 --> 00:07:58,600
What?

143
00:08:06,650 --> 00:08:07,700
You're lost.

144
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:14,040
You made a Li Palace Sword Formation,
with only Realm of Seated Illumination.

145
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:15,040
That was amazing.

146
00:08:15,200 --> 00:08:16,540
However, in order to pursue precision,

147
00:08:16,540 --> 00:08:18,320
you forced on some extra construction,

148
00:08:18,320 --> 00:08:19,780
which left flaws instead.

149
00:08:19,960 --> 00:08:20,940
In my opinion,

150
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:22,600
if we change the formation into this,

151
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:24,660
it will be perfect and more powerful.

152
00:08:31,180 --> 00:08:32,990
Not only did he see my weakness,

153
00:08:33,549 --> 00:08:36,159
but he also improved my formation
in the battle.

154
00:08:36,159 --> 00:08:37,240
More importantly,

155
00:08:37,760 --> 00:08:39,270
the reformed formation

156
00:08:39,450 --> 00:08:41,580
has a more concise and orderly beauty.

157
00:08:41,919 --> 00:08:42,919
That's really...

158
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:44,520
wonderful!

159
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:51,680
I admit my defeat.

160
00:08:51,920 --> 00:08:52,520
Everyone,

161
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:53,180
please.

162
00:08:58,640 --> 00:09:00,770
Chen Changsheng is indeed a director.

163
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:01,960
Grand Pontiff

164
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:04,140
your judgment is truly exceptional.

165
00:09:07,280 --> 00:09:08,540
What should we do next?

166
00:09:09,640 --> 00:09:10,570
It's just ahead.

167
00:09:10,680 --> 00:09:11,800
The Green Leaf World

168
00:09:11,800 --> 00:09:13,520
is a small world transformed from

169
00:09:13,520 --> 00:09:14,880
the Five-Leaf Flower
in Grand Pontiff's hand.

170
00:09:14,880 --> 00:09:16,880
The entrance is certainly unusual.

171
00:09:21,520 --> 00:09:23,120
Are you playing tricks on us?

172
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:25,600
Please rest assured.

173
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:27,970
Flowers in a mirrow; the moon in the water;

174
00:09:27,970 --> 00:09:29,680
unconcerned with coming or going.

175
00:09:29,680 --> 00:09:31,080
The pool is the entrance.

176
00:09:45,730 --> 00:09:47,120
I didn't expect a small leaf

177
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:49,040
to carry such a vast world.

178
00:09:48,820 --> 00:09:52,060
[Green Leaf World]

179
00:09:49,800 --> 00:09:50,330
Let's go.

180
00:09:50,760 --> 00:09:51,760
Let's go find Luo.

181
00:09:56,190 --> 00:09:58,880
[Five-Leaf Flower]

182
00:09:58,940 --> 00:10:01,500
He even gave the treasure of the religion

183
00:10:01,530 --> 00:10:03,580
to that child.

184
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:07,090
It seems that he really values him.

185
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:10,620
He was thrown into the Abandoned Courtyard
when he just came to Shendu.

186
00:10:10,620 --> 00:10:13,140
Recently, the Tianhai family
has been suppressing him.

187
00:10:13,140 --> 00:10:15,860
Plus, there was the dragon
from Tong Palace.

188
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:17,870
Are we putting

189
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:19,920
too much pressure on him?

190
00:10:20,310 --> 00:10:21,600
You feel sorry for him?

191
00:10:21,620 --> 00:10:24,850
He's a promising young man.

192
00:10:25,280 --> 00:10:26,320
Not enough.

193
00:10:26,910 --> 00:10:28,820
Since he's that person's disciple,

194
00:10:28,820 --> 00:10:32,110
all these hardships are necessary.

195
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:40,240
Your Highness.

196
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:41,410
The food is cold.

197
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:43,020
Let me change it for you.

198
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:44,540
I don't want to eat.

199
00:10:44,560 --> 00:10:45,690
Just leave it there.

200
00:10:48,850 --> 00:10:50,510
[I miss you]

201
00:10:52,130 --> 00:10:53,320
So annoying.

202
00:10:54,280 --> 00:10:55,660
Master is not here.

203
00:10:55,690 --> 00:10:57,530
I just can't focus on anything.

204
00:10:58,830 --> 00:11:00,350
I said I'm not eating!

205
00:11:00,800 --> 00:11:02,010
Then, I'll take it.

206
00:11:04,800 --> 00:11:05,970
Xuanyuan Po!

207
00:11:06,400 --> 00:11:07,400
Tang Thirty-Six!

208
00:11:08,520 --> 00:11:09,920
Master is not here.

209
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,000
Sir!

210
00:11:16,680 --> 00:11:17,160
Luo.

211
00:11:18,160 --> 00:11:19,260
You're here!

212
00:11:21,920 --> 00:11:23,080
Bai Luoheng is here.

213
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:24,060
Greetings, Sir.

214
00:11:24,920 --> 00:11:26,380
You seem to have improved.

215
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:27,990
How have you been?

216
00:11:28,400 --> 00:11:29,080
Me?

217
00:11:29,160 --> 00:11:30,580
There are many classics
and treasures here,

218
00:11:30,580 --> 00:11:31,660
and the food is delicious.

219
00:11:31,660 --> 00:11:32,900
I'm doing very well!

220
00:11:34,770 --> 00:11:37,030
But it seems you haven't eaten anything.

221
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:38,640
Dear,

222
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:40,240
-Crossed out.
-Tang Tang!

223
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:42,240
-Don't go through others' stuff!
-Respected Master,

224
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:43,230
How are you?

225
00:11:44,060 --> 00:11:45,800
I'm in Green Leaf World.

226
00:11:46,040 --> 00:11:47,230
It's huge here,

227
00:11:47,260 --> 00:11:48,610
and the view is beautiful.

228
00:11:48,610 --> 00:11:50,420
But without you,

229
00:11:50,470 --> 00:11:52,720
the bigger the world is,
the lonelier I feel.

230
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:53,840
Give it back!

231
00:12:01,160 --> 00:12:02,220
It's just a letter.

232
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:03,320
Are you serious?

233
00:12:06,160 --> 00:12:07,680
I didn't mean it.

234
00:12:07,680 --> 00:12:08,560
I just...

235
00:12:09,090 --> 00:12:10,200
I just...

236
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:12,080
miss you.

237
00:12:13,160 --> 00:12:15,370
We're here to pick you up
for the Imperial Court Exam.

238
00:12:15,370 --> 00:12:16,320
Do you want to go?

239
00:12:16,340 --> 00:12:17,630
Not just that.

240
00:12:17,660 --> 00:12:18,990
I've even found the way.

241
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:20,480
Follow me.

242
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:21,680
This is the shortcut.

243
00:12:27,280 --> 00:12:27,960
Sir.

244
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:28,680
Come on!

245
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:33,890
Go!

246
00:12:33,910 --> 00:12:35,520
The cleric there dare not stop me.

247
00:12:35,520 --> 00:12:37,000
As long as we don't run into...

248
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:38,440
Cardinal...

249
00:12:41,520 --> 00:12:42,160
Cardinal,

250
00:12:42,520 --> 00:12:43,440
I'm here to take Luo

251
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:44,640
for the Imperial Court Exam.

252
00:12:44,640 --> 00:12:45,440
The State Religious Academy

253
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:46,120
needs her.

254
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:47,800
Don't worry.

255
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:51,320
Li Palace won't restrict
Her Highness's freedom.

256
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:53,520
On the day of the Imperial Court Exam,

257
00:12:53,520 --> 00:12:55,840
I'll escort her over there in person.

258
00:12:55,960 --> 00:12:56,960
What do you think?

259
00:12:57,440 --> 00:12:58,810
Thank you, Cardinal.

260
00:12:59,320 --> 00:13:00,360
Do you know

261
00:13:00,520 --> 00:13:02,960
why you are here?

262
00:13:04,720 --> 00:13:05,640
Since Li Palace

263
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:08,000
didn't make things difficult for Luo,

264
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:09,440
is the person you want to see

265
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:10,280
actually me?

266
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:12,880
Yes.

267
00:13:13,160 --> 00:13:14,520
You're smart.

268
00:13:15,160 --> 00:13:18,520
We've arranged
an interesting test for you.

269
00:13:18,960 --> 00:13:19,880
What test?

270
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:22,400
I've prepared it for you.

271
00:13:22,640 --> 00:13:24,040
Walk out of here,

272
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:26,160
and you'll see.

273
00:13:34,880 --> 00:13:36,280
There are so many people.

274
00:13:36,280 --> 00:13:38,340
Are they going to let you fight again?

275
00:13:39,280 --> 00:13:40,920
The people
from the State Religious Academy are here.

276
00:13:40,920 --> 00:13:42,040
Why are they here?

277
00:13:43,680 --> 00:13:44,960
Hey, the second son of the Wenshui family!

278
00:13:44,960 --> 00:13:47,090
You're from such a worthless academy.

279
00:13:47,560 --> 00:13:48,080
What?

280
00:13:48,280 --> 00:13:49,040
Do you want to fight?

281
00:13:49,040 --> 00:13:50,150
The Blue Cloud List is changing.

282
00:13:49,870 --> 00:13:52,450
[Ye Xiaolian, 41st on Blue Cloud List,
Disciple of the Saintess Peak]

283
00:13:50,170 --> 00:13:51,700
Aren't they ashamed

284
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:52,920
to come and watch the event?

285
00:13:52,920 --> 00:13:54,720
The Blue Cloud List is changing?

286
00:13:54,720 --> 00:13:55,920
You're not qualified

287
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:57,580
to run wild here.

288
00:14:00,360 --> 00:14:02,960
There are countless masters
on the Continent,

289
00:14:03,120 --> 00:14:06,360
but geniuses always emerge in their youth.

290
00:14:03,830 --> 00:14:04,740
[First place]

291
00:14:05,260 --> 00:14:05,860
[Xu Yourong]

292
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:08,320
The Heavenly Destiny Pavilion

293
00:14:08,320 --> 00:14:10,920
sets up a ranking list

294
00:14:10,920 --> 00:14:12,920
for those who are under 20

295
00:14:11,270 --> 00:14:13,480
[Qin Mochen]

296
00:14:13,240 --> 00:14:14,840
to encourage the young.

297
00:14:16,550 --> 00:14:16,960
[Duan Xiu]

298
00:14:17,080 --> 00:14:19,960
All of you should work hard

299
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:17,610
[Zhao Jinyun]

300
00:14:17,610 --> 00:14:17,990
[Zhong Hui]

301
00:14:18,040 --> 00:14:18,390
[Qi Jian]

302
00:14:18,410 --> 00:14:18,650
[Li Zhao]

303
00:14:18,660 --> 00:14:18,950
[Liang Banhu]

304
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:19,270
[Guan Feibai]

305
00:14:19,340 --> 00:14:19,580
[Bai Cai]

306
00:14:19,640 --> 00:14:20,000
[Liang Xiaoxiao]

307
00:14:20,260 --> 00:14:20,740
[Zhe Xiu]

308
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:23,160
to make your name on the list.

309
00:14:21,520 --> 00:14:22,450
[Xu Yourong]

310
00:14:22,510 --> 00:14:22,570
[Guan Feibai]

311
00:14:28,920 --> 00:14:29,760
Elder of Heavenly Destiny!

312
00:14:29,190 --> 00:14:31,430
[Elder of Heavenly Destiny,
Head of Storms from Eight Directions]

313
00:14:31,800 --> 00:14:32,740
By tradition,

314
00:14:32,760 --> 00:14:34,380
it's not the time to announce the list.

315
00:14:34,380 --> 00:14:36,440
Is this the Cardinal's arrangement?

316
00:14:36,440 --> 00:14:38,280
Senior, you've improved
your cultivation recently.

317
00:14:38,280 --> 00:14:39,840
It must be you who made it.

318
00:14:41,880 --> 00:14:43,170
It's simple.

319
00:14:43,560 --> 00:14:44,160
Look!

320
00:14:44,320 --> 00:14:46,590
[Su Moyu]

321
00:14:44,400 --> 00:14:45,880
Senior Su ranks 33,

322
00:14:45,920 --> 00:14:47,680
comfortably ahead of Tang Thirty-Six.

323
00:14:47,680 --> 00:14:50,810
You must be the one
who's improved the fastest this time.

324
00:14:51,880 --> 00:14:54,200
Students, many of you have improved.

325
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:55,680
Congratulations.

326
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:57,520
However, the events to come

327
00:14:57,760 --> 00:15:00,160
will concern the State Religious Academy.

328
00:15:01,360 --> 00:15:04,320
I hereby announce
the newcomers on the list.

329
00:15:05,320 --> 00:15:07,200
From the State Religious Academy,

330
00:15:07,200 --> 00:15:08,750
Xuanyuan Po!

331
00:15:10,400 --> 00:15:11,130
Impossible!

332
00:15:13,040 --> 00:15:13,650
Me?

333
00:15:13,800 --> 00:15:15,460
He gave up on us, the Zhaixing Academy.

334
00:15:15,460 --> 00:15:16,760
How could he get on the list?

335
00:15:16,530 --> 00:15:17,490
[Xuanyuan Po]

336
00:15:17,750 --> 00:15:20,470
He ranks 148.

337
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:19,450
[Xuanyuan Po]

338
00:15:27,840 --> 00:15:28,480
Me?

339
00:15:28,520 --> 00:15:29,360
It's me?

340
00:15:29,600 --> 00:15:30,160
Sir.

341
00:15:30,550 --> 00:15:31,170
Sir!

342
00:15:31,400 --> 00:15:33,890
I'm on the Blue Cloud List!

343
00:15:38,580 --> 00:15:39,680
I'm on the Blue Cloud List!

344
00:15:39,680 --> 00:15:43,000
Now announcing the fast climber!

345
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:44,880
From the State Religious Academy,

346
00:15:44,880 --> 00:15:46,000
Tang Tang.

347
00:15:48,760 --> 00:15:49,960
It's you, Tang Tang!

348
00:15:50,350 --> 00:15:51,410
Congratulations.

349
00:15:51,800 --> 00:15:53,920
His final rank is

350
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:52,720
[Tang Tang]

351
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:57,580
[Tang Tang]

352
00:15:54,520 --> 00:15:56,800
Blue Cloud 16!

353
00:15:59,680 --> 00:16:00,600
Genius.

354
00:16:00,620 --> 00:16:02,760
I can only describe myself with this word!

355
00:16:02,760 --> 00:16:05,120
The newly ranked second on the list.

356
00:16:05,560 --> 00:16:06,420
Second?

357
00:16:06,920 --> 00:16:09,680
I can't believe someone can beat
the genius, Zhe Xiu.

358
00:16:09,680 --> 00:16:11,440
From the State Religious Academy,

359
00:16:11,440 --> 00:16:12,840
Bai Luoheng.

360
00:16:15,100 --> 00:16:17,080
[Bai Luoheng]

361
00:16:16,080 --> 00:16:17,240
She goes up

362
00:16:17,840 --> 00:16:19,560
to the second place on Blue Cloud.

363
00:16:18,540 --> 00:16:20,990
[Bai Luoheng]

364
00:16:21,280 --> 00:16:21,880
Luo!

365
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:23,790
Her Highness is extraordinary!

366
00:16:23,790 --> 00:16:25,710
[Bai Luoheng]

367
00:16:25,710 --> 00:16:27,630
[Xu Yourong]

368
00:16:27,880 --> 00:16:29,160
Xuanyuan Po,

369
00:16:29,360 --> 00:16:30,400
Tang Tang,

370
00:16:30,400 --> 00:16:33,040
and Bai Luoheng have met a good teacher

371
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:35,520
and quickly rose on the Blue Cloud List.

372
00:16:35,590 --> 00:16:38,600
We can also look forward
to their future achievement.

373
00:16:38,720 --> 00:16:40,520
They only been in the
State Religious Academy for a short time,

374
00:16:40,520 --> 00:16:41,800
and they're already this strong!

375
00:16:41,800 --> 00:16:44,160
Well then, isn't Chen Changsheng
who taught them more...

376
00:16:44,160 --> 00:16:45,820
I want to be his disciple, too.

377
00:16:46,240 --> 00:16:46,840
Thank you,

378
00:16:47,040 --> 00:16:47,840
good teacher!

379
00:16:48,480 --> 00:16:51,080
Director, thank you
for treating my injuries.

380
00:16:51,560 --> 00:16:54,010
The Cardinal said
he had prepared a test for me.

381
00:16:54,010 --> 00:16:56,740
Is it related to the change
of the Blue Cloud List?

382
00:16:57,080 --> 00:16:57,960
Everyone,

383
00:16:58,560 --> 00:17:01,560
there is another hopeful candidate today.

384
00:17:03,480 --> 00:17:07,210
He wants to compete with all the geniuses
in the Imperial Court Exam

385
00:17:07,670 --> 00:17:10,220
and aim for first place!

386
00:17:15,880 --> 00:17:17,000
He is

387
00:17:18,200 --> 00:17:19,630
from the State Religious Academy.

388
00:17:19,460 --> 00:17:21,060
[Chen Changsheng]

389
00:17:20,359 --> 00:17:22,200
Chen Changsheng!

390
00:17:21,060 --> 00:17:23,960
[Chen Changsheng] [Xu Yourong]

391
00:17:27,990 --> 00:17:30,470
[Chen Changsheng] [Xu Yourong]

392
00:17:33,610 --> 00:17:35,690
[Ascending to Blue Cloud together]

393
00:17:35,720 --> 00:17:38,240
[The Wind Rises Among the Ivy, Episode 8]

394
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:40,360
Chen Changsheng.

395
00:17:40,600 --> 00:17:41,920
At the Imperial Court Exam,

396
00:17:41,920 --> 00:17:43,640
I'll take you down a peg!

397
00:17:48,120 --> 00:17:49,990
Don't you know your place?

398
00:17:50,010 --> 00:17:51,400
The first place

399
00:17:51,400 --> 00:17:53,600
will only belong to our Southern Realm!

400
00:18:09,200 --> 00:18:11,200
Chen Changsheng is really bold.

401
00:18:17,760 --> 00:18:19,120
Chen Changsheng,

402
00:18:20,040 --> 00:18:24,080
I look forward to your performance
in the Imperial Court Exam.

403
00:18:24,640 --> 00:18:27,080
He wants to win the first place
with only the Realm of Marrow Cleansing?

404
00:18:27,080 --> 00:18:28,120
How arrogant!

405
00:18:28,200 --> 00:18:29,320
Are you insulting us?

406
00:18:29,320 --> 00:18:30,500
Is he insulting us?

407
00:18:30,760 --> 00:18:32,020
After him saying that,

408
00:18:32,360 --> 00:18:35,520
I'll be the target of everyone
in the Imperial Court Exam.

409
00:18:35,520 --> 00:18:37,760
This is the test the Cardinal meant.

410
00:18:44,120 --> 00:18:46,920
The Qingteng Banquet
is just the appetizer,

411
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:49,720
and the Imperial Court Exam
is the main course.

412
00:18:49,720 --> 00:18:51,880
How far can you go,

413
00:18:52,280 --> 00:18:54,000
Chen Changsheng?

414
00:18:55,130 --> 00:18:59,230
[To be continued]

415
00:19:00,190 --> 00:19:01,700
Don't you all want more?

416
00:19:01,720 --> 00:19:03,860
I asked the white crane
to bring you a surprise.

417
00:19:03,860 --> 00:19:05,660
Please scan the QR code to watch.

418
00:19:07,320 --> 00:19:08,620
To win in the Imperial Court Exam,

419
00:19:07,370 --> 00:19:10,440
[In the next episode]

420
00:19:08,680 --> 00:19:10,960
I can only have a chance
by reaching Seated Illumination.

421
00:19:10,960 --> 00:19:13,490
Actually, I had no choice
from the beginning.

422
00:19:14,520 --> 00:19:16,290
I helped you out last time.

423
00:19:16,480 --> 00:19:17,200
This time,

424
00:19:17,220 --> 00:19:18,820
it's your turn to help me out.

425
00:19:19,080 --> 00:19:20,290
I don't have confidence,

426
00:19:20,290 --> 00:19:21,610
but I will do my best.

427
00:19:22,240 --> 00:19:22,880
Come on!

428
00:19:23,640 --> 00:19:24,560
Break this formation!

